Icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) kiza kwiyongera cyane mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kuva tariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Ibitera koronavirus (COVID-19) byo mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza, bigaragaza ko nubwo ubwandu bwa COVID-19 buri mu bihugu bitandukanye, bugenda bukwirakwira mu bihugu byose.
Mu rwego rwo kwitegura ku buryo bufatika, ibihugu, ibitaro n'imiryango y'abarwayi b'indwara yihariye, bagombye kurushaho kwitegura ku buryo bufatika icyorezo cya COVID-19 kizacyura abantu benshi bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bw'ibanze.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2020, mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, habayeho umubare munini w'abarwayi ba Pneumonia bafite impamvu zitazwi.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara mu Bushinwa cyatangaje ko iyi ndwara ari icyorezo gishya cya Coronavirus, kuva icyo gihe ikaba yitwa Coronavirus 2 syndrome y'ubuhumekero bukabije cyangwa SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, uburwayi bwatewe no kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bwiswe icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ibitabo by'ubu bushakashatsi bigaragaza ko abagera kuri 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 bagerwaho n'indwara y'ubuhumekero, haba mu gihe bafite cyangwa badafite pneumonia, kandi abenshi muri bo bakira.
Mu bice 14%, COVID-19 yabaye indwara ikomeye cyane, aho abarwayi bagombaga kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe 6% by'abasigaye bari barwaye indwara ikomeye cyane, bajyanywe mu bitaro by'indembe.
Umubare w'abapfa bazira COVID-19 uri ku kigero cya 4%.
Muri iki cyifuzo, twasuzumye uko COVID-19 ikwirakwira mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Igihugu cy'ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, maze turagereranya uko byagenze mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya umubare w'abantu banduye COVID-19 muri EU/Economic Area n'u Bwongereza n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva tariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Ibihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Nyuma y'aho, COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu bice byinshi by'isi, kandi ingendo z'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ubu zikurikiza uko byagenze muri iki gihugu.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko hari icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Mu kinyamakuru cyasohowe ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe 2020 cyitwa Eurosurveillance, Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje ko ari we muntu wa mbere w'i Burayi wafashwe na Coronavirus nk'uko byemezwa n'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Igihugu cy'ubukungu bw'u Burayi, ku wa 24 Mutarama 2020 nibwo aba mbere banduye mu gihugu cy'u Bufaransa bagaragaye mu bavuye i Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, mu bihugu byose 30 by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza (Ubwongereza), abantu banduye COVID-19 bamaze kumenyekana, ku buryo ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza ku iherezo ry'uwo munsi, hatangajwe abantu 39,768 banduye n'abantu 1,727 banduye, naho mu Butaliyani honyine habayeho abantu 1,7750 banduye n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye.
Gutanga amakuru ku bantu banduye COVID-19
Mu Kigo cy'Ibihugu by'i Burayi Gishinzwe Kugenzura no Gukumira Indwara (ECDC), imibare y'abarwaye COVID-19 yemejwe mu bihugu byose byo ku isi, igera ku isaha ya saa munani z'ijoro, igatangwa buri munsi n'ibiro by'ubuyobozi, urugero nk'ibiro by'Ubuzima, inzego z'igihugu n'ibanze z'ubuzima muri ibyo bihugu ndetse n'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima.
Ibi byatangajwe mu rwego rwo gupima imikorere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza no kugereranya n'u Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo kumenya umubare w'abantu bafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19, twagerageje kugabanya igihe cyo kwiyongera cy'iminsi 14 ku barwayi ba COVID-19, bityo igihe cyo kwiyongera kwa COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 cy'iminsi, mu bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Igihugu cy'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibipimo by'abarwayi bo mu bihugu bitandukanye byagereranyijwe n'iby'abantu bose bari mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubuzima ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Ibihugu by'ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Ibipimo by'iminsi 14 y'ubukungu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, byiganjemo ibipimo by'ubuhinzi bw'i Hubei mu Bushinwa (ishusho ya 1).
Muri rusange, mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Igihugu cy'ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangiye ku wa 21 Gashyantare, nyuma kiza kwiyongera cyane ku wa 28 Gashyantare 2020 (ibikubiye mu ngingo).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'umubare w'abapfuye bagaragaye mu Butaliyani wiyongereye cyane, ariko ibihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Igihugu cy'ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza na byo byerekanye ko hari ukwiyongera nk'uko byagenze mu gihe habaga habayeho icyorezo cya COVID-19 (bisabwa).
Mu ishusho ya 2, hagaragajwe ko umubare w'abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Igihugu cy'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranywa n'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Iyo raporo ivuga ko ku isaha ya saa munani z'ijoro ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibindi bihugu 15 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Economic Area (EEA) hamwe n'u Bwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abantu banduye, ugereranywa n'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu cyangwa birenga.
Ibisubizo byacu bigaragaza ko umubare w'abarwaye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Ibihugu by'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza wiyongera cyane.
Uko ibintu byifashe mu gihe COVID-19 ikomeje kwiyongera, bigaragaza ko icyorezo kizakwira mu bihugu byose ku muvuduko umwe.
Ibi nubwo ibihugu bikunze guhura n'ibihe bitandukanye by'icyorezo, hari itandukaniro mu buryo abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage b'ibihugu bitabira ibi bibazo, kandi mu bihugu bitandukanye hari ibipimo bitandukanye by'abantu bagomba gukora ikizamini cyo kwemeza cyangwa ikizamini cy'inyongera cya COVID-19.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bice byanduye by'Ubutaliyani batangaje ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwaye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho by'umwihariko, kandi itangazamakuru ryavuze ko ubushobozi bw'ibitaro n'amazu y'ubuvuzi yihariye muri ibyo bice bwaramaze kuzuzwa.
Kugeza ubu, mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Afurika y'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, mu bice 6% na 1% by'ibihugu, amakuru ajyanye no kujya kwa muganga no/cyangwa kujya kwa muganga ku barwayi ba COVID-19 (amakuru ntabwo agaragara).
Ariko kandi, bagomba gufatwa uko bikwiye kugira ngo bakoreshe amakuru y'ubugenzuzi nk'agasohozwa, bagamije kwibanda ku bice byinshi by'imibereho y'abapfuye n'iy'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko hari itandukaniro rikomeye ku bijyanye no kubona ibitaro by'ubuvuzi bwihariye n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bigezweho mu Burayi, aho ibitaro by'ubuvuzi bingana na 29.2 mu Budage, bigera kuri 4.2 muri Porutugali ku bantu 100.000.
Ibi bivuze ko ibyo bihugu bifite uburyo bwinshi cyangwa buke kurusha u Butaliyani (ibibanza 12.5 by'uburwayi bwihariye n'ibisanzwe ku baturage 100.000 mu mwaka wa 2010-2011).
Imimerere yo gukora ingero y'ibipimo by'ubuzima n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi, hamwe n'ibipimo by'ibihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Igihugu cy'ubukungu n'Ubwongereza ku ndwara ya COVID-19 ifite ibyago > 90% byo kurenga ubushobozi bw'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bwihariye, byatanzwe mu igenamigambi rya gatandatu ry'igenzura ry'ibyago byihutirwa rya ECDC ku bijyanye na COVID-19.
Kubera ko abantu banduye bamaze kugaragara mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ibihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Igihugu cy'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza, kandi ko ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bwihariye bigakorera abaturage bo mu karere, amakuru ku bantu banduye n'amazu y'ubuvuzi bwihariye agomba gutangwa hakurikijwe uburyo bw'ibipimo by'ubwenegihugu ku rwego rwa 2 (NUTS-2).
Imibereho y'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani n'imikorere iriho mu bindi bihugu, bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kigenda gitera imbere mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Ibihugu by'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bwihariye bigomba rero kwitegura guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ihindagurika ry'abantu benshi banduye SARS-CoV-2 no gutanga uburyo bwo kwakira abarwayi banduye COVID-19, cyane cyane mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bwihariye, nk'uko byagenze mu bice byanduye by'u Butaliyani.
Mu igenzura ry'ibyago byihuta rya ECDC riherutse gukorwa, hagaragajwe ko ari ngombwa ko hashyirwaho ingamba zihuse, z'imbere kandi zihariye zo guhangana n'icyorezo, kugira ngo icyorezo cyandura vuba, cyongere gihagarare, ndetse n'imikorere yacyo ihinduke, kuko mu gihe hatagize ingamba zifatika, umubare w'abarwaye ushobora kwiyongera vuba, bityo ibigo by'abashinga ibyemezo n'ibitaro bikaba bitarabona uburyo buhagije bwo kumenya, kwakira no gushyira mu bikorwa ibisubizo bikwiye.
Iperereza ry'ibyago ririmo no gushyira mu bikorwa ingamba z'ubuzima bw'abaturage zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Ibihugu bifite umwanya muto wo kongera imbaraga mu bikorwa byo kugenzura no kugabanya umuvuduko w'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2, bityo bigatuma ingufu z'ubuvuzi zigabanuka.
Mu gihe ibyo bidashoboka, gahunda z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Ibihugu by'ubukungu bw'u Burayi zishobora guhura n'imivurungano y'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) cyatewe na Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) indwara ifata abantu benshi cyane (SARS), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga ibihumbi bitatu n'indwara zisaga ibihumbi 80 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, kandi byahitanye abantu benshi.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kuba yaranduye abantu ibihumbi n'ibihumbi mu 2003 ikoresheje ibihuha, nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV, ikoresheje uburyo busa n'ubwo, ikagira ibimenyetso bisa n'ibyo.
Nubwo COVID-19 ifite ubukana buke ugereranyije na SARS, ariko ifite ubukana bwinshi, kandi ishobora kwandura abantu bakuze n'abagabo kurusha abakiri bato n'abagore.
Mu gusubiza ku bitabo byinshi bivuga kuri iyi ndwara, iyi nkunga yagerageje gutanga ibitekerezo mu buryo bw'igihe kandi buhagije ku bushakashatsi ku iyi ndwara.
Tuzabaha amakuru y'ibanze ku bijyanye n'icyorezo, etiologie, virologie, gupima, kuvura, kubamenyesha no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo ibibazo byinshi bikiri ibisubizo, iki cyifuzo ni uko iki gikorwa kizaba ari ingirakamaro mu kumenya iyi ndwara iteje akaga no kuyikuraho.
Umunsi mukuru w'ihangu ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye umunsi w'ingenzi cyane ku Bashinwa basabwe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cy'iminsi mikuru yose n'ibyumweru byinshi nyuma yaho kubera icyorezo cy'indwara ya virusi nshya.
Iyi virusi ifite isano rya bugufi na Coronavirus (CoV) yateje icyorezo cya SARS mu mwaka wa 2003, niyo mpamvu ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryahisemo ko ari SARS-CoV-2 n'icyorezo giherekejwe nacyo, COVID-19 (indwara ya Coronavirus-19 cyangwa COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, gikwira igihugu cyose ndetse n'ibindi bihugu 5 ku isi hose.
Kuva ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, iyi virusi yaviramo abantu barenga 80,000 banduye burundu, umubare w'abarwayi bavurwa urenga 40,000, ndetse hapfa abantu barenga 3,000.
"Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima ku isi (OMS) ryagaragaje ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere w'abantu bose" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba".
Nk'uko bigaragara mububiko bw'amakuru bwa PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hasohotse ibitabo by'ubumenyi birenga 200 byerekeranye na COVID-19, birimo ibiganiro birimo ubushakashatsi ku bijyanye n'indwara z'agakoko, icyorezo, ihindagurika ry'umubiri, indwara, indwara n'ubuvuzi kuva aho inkuru ya mbere yo ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yerekeye kugenome y'abantu benshi bagizwe ingero y'indwara ya COVID-19 yashyizwe ahagaragara.
Iki gitabo kigamije gusuzuma mu buryo bw'ibanze iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi mu nzego nshya.
Mu bice bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara ya coronavirus yitwa syndrome respiratoire ya Middle East (indwara ya SARS yandutse mu mwaka wa 2012).
Tuzasuzuma ibyo twigishijwe ku birebana no kwirinda no kwirinda indwara, ndetse n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi bikiriho.
Coronavirus zakunze kugaragara ko ari indwara zitera indwara zitera indwara z'ubwonko, kandi ziterwa na 15% by'indwara z'ibicurane.
Icyakora, mu kinyejana gishize, twahuye na koronavirusi zanduye cyane, ari zo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, incuro ebyiri zose, zikaba ari zo zatumye indwara zanduza mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, zikaza no mu bindi bihugu mu gihe gito, zikaba zarateye indwara nyinshi, urupfu n'urupfu.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya Coronavirus cyigaragaje mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu ishusho ya 1, imibare y'ibicurane by'ubushongi bitagaragara byatangajwe bwa mbere muri Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu y'u Bushinwa, ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan.
Hashize iminsi irindwi, icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyakwirakwiriye.
Ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020, nibwo habonetse ubwandu bwa mbere bw'ibinyabuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi ituwe n'abaturage, mu bindi bihugu no mu ntara.
