Coronavirus ni umuryango muto w'indwara nini cyane kandi z'ubwirakabiri zifite umurongo umwe w'urundi rukomeye wa RNA.
Zigabanywa mu bwoko bune aribwo alfa, beta, gamma na delta, harimo coronavirus zandura abantu ari zo alfa na beta.
Glycoprotein Spike (S) ikingira virusi ya SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, ikorana n'ibikoresho byayo by'ubwonko bihuza ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwonko, ari zo angiotensin 2 (ACE2) na dipeptideyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) bihindura ingirabuzimafatizo.
Igitekerezo cya RNA cya virusi gisigazwa mu cyotoplasma; nyuma yo kwongera igitsina cya virusi, RNA ya virusi hamwe n'ibisonga bya glycoproteins na proteins za nucleoacids, bivamo viscule zirimo virion, hanyuma zikajya zihurira n'uruhu rwa plasma, bigatuma virusi nshya isohoka.
Icyiciro cya mbere cy'ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 cyatangajwe ku itariki ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
Ibyavuye muri iyi raporo bigaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ari ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus beta, ifite ibyakorewe 10 by'ubwoko bw'ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa mbere ku isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Hunan mu mujyi wa Wuhan, bifite ibisaga 99.98.
Virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ifite byinshi ihuriyeho na SARS-CoV mu mibereho yayo mu rwego rwa genetika ugereranyije na MERS-CoV.
