Basanze iyo kompanyi ifite imiterere y'ubwisanzure, igenda ihinduka dimer, maze kompanyi ACE2-B0AT1 ikaba ishobora guhuza na poroteyine ebyiri za S, zishobora gukoreshwa nk'urugero rwo gutahura no kwandura coronavirus.
