Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kizaza
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatewe na Coronavirus SARS-CoV-2 gikomeje kwiyongera.
"Nubwo ijambo ""icyorezo"" ryerekeza gusa ku rugero rw'icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye, nta kintu na kimwe kigaragaza ko hari ibintu byihariye bishobora gutera akaga, OMS yavuze ko ari ngombwa ko leta ziteza imbere ibi bikurikira:
"Ibihugu byose bishobora guhinduka".
Tedros Adhanom, umuyobozi w'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima, avuga ko "ibihugu bigomba kugira icyo bigeraho mu gihe byita ku bantu, ku barwayi, ku barwayi, ku barwayi, ku barwayi, ku barwayi no ku baganga".
"Turi mu kaga cyane ku rugero rw'umuburo wo kugabanuka kw'icyorezo n'uburemere bwacyo ndetse no ku rugero rw'umuburo wo kutagira icyo ukora".
Dr. Tom Friedman, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Gishinzwe Kugabanya Indwara n'Ikibuza Indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo cyari " kitigeze kibaho".
Yagize ati "mu itangazo CNN yasohoye mu kwezi kwa kabiri, nta wundi virusi yo mu mpumuro yigeze ivugwa kuva igihe ibimenyetso by'indwara ya grippe byabonetse kugeza igihe icyorezo cy'icyorezo cyakomeje kwiyongera ku isi".
Ghebreyesus yavuze amagambo nk'ayo, agira ati "Nta ndwara y'icyorezo ya Coronavirus twigeze tubona.
Yakomeje agira ati "Nta kindi gihe twigeze tubona icyorezo cy'indwara cyashoboraga guhangana n'iki cyorezo icyarimwe".
Icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane cyakurikiye icyemezo cy'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) cyatangaje ko mu kwezi kwa mbere iki cyorezo cy'indwara ya Covid-19 cyabaye ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'abaturage ku rwego mpuzamahanga.
Dr Anthony Fosse, umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Imitsi n'Amatwara y'Amatwara muri Amerika, yavuze ko "mu by'ukuri ibintu bigenda birushaho kuzamba".
Kuva kuwa kane, Associated Press yatangaje ko ku isi hose hari abantu bagera ku 126,000 banduye COVID-19, bihitana abantu barenga 4.600.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2020-2019 ni icyorezo cy'indwara ya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) cyatewe n'indwara yo guhumeka ikaze ya Coronavirus 2 (SARS-COVID-2).
Icyorezo cya Virusi ya Wuhan cyagaragaye mu kwezi k'Ukuboza 2019 mu Bushinwa, cyatangajwe ku wa 30 Mutarama 2020 nk'icyorezo cy'indwara y'uburwayi ku rwego rw'igihugu, cyatangajwe ku wa 11 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bituma abantu bagera ku 97.000 bapfa.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 ni bo bamaze gukira.
Umubare w'abapfa mu Bushinwa wari ugereranyije na 4%, ariko ku isi hose, wari kuva kuri 13.4% muri Algeria kugera kuri 0.08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso by'ibisanzwe birimo umuriro, guhinda umushyitsi no guhumeka nabi.
Indwara z'indwara z'ubwonko zirimo ubumuga bwo mu gituza (pneumonia) n'indwara yo guhumeka cyane (Acute respiratory distress syndrome).
Guhera igihe umuntu agaragaye ko afite virusi kugeza igihe bimenyetso byigaragaye, bimara iminsi igera kuri itanu, ariko bishobora gutandukana kuva ku minsi ibiri kugeza ku minsi cumi n'ine.
Nta nkingo cyangwa umuti wa virusi uhagije ufasha indwara.
Mu by'ukuri, uburyo bwo kwivuza bwa mbere ni uburyo bwo kuvura ibimenyetso n'ubufasha. Ingamba zo kwirinda zigirwa, harimo gukaraba intoki, guhuma mu kanwa igihe uvuye mu kanwa, kwirinda abandi, no gusuzuma no gushyira mu kato abantu bakekwaho kuba banduye.
Abayobozi ku isi hose bitabiriye ibihano byo guhagarika ingendo, kuziba abantu, guhagarika ingendo, kugenzura ibyago byo mu kazi no kureka imirimo.
Iki cyorezo cy'indwara y'icyorezo cyatumye isi yose ihungabana mu by'imibereho n'ubukungu, ibikorwa by'imikino, iby'idini, ibya politiki n'iby'umuco bigatinda cyangwa bigatinda, ndetse n'ubukene bw'umutungo ku buryo bukomeye, bitewe n'ubwoba bwo guhaha.
Amashuri na kaminuza yafunzwe mu bihugu 193 haba ku rwego rw'igihugu cyangwa mu karere, bigira ingaruka ku kigero cya 99.4% cy'abari mu mashuri ku isi.
Amakuru atari yo kuri iyi virusi yagiye asohoka ku mbuga nkoranyambaga, ndetse n'ibindi byago by'iterabwoba n'ivangura byibasira Abashinwa, abandi bantu bafite ubwoko n'ubwoko, bo mu Burasirazuba n'Amajyepfo y'Iburasirazuba bwa Aziya n'ahandi hantu habayeho ubwandu bwinshi.
Ingendo zigabanutse n'ibihe by'akaruhuko by'inganda ndende, umwuka mubi n'umwuka wa karuboni byagabanutse.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, abategetsi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa (umurwa mukuru w'intara ya Hubei) batangaje ko hari abantu banduye indwara ya pneumonia y'ubwonko itarigera itangwa, kandi iperereza ryatangiye mu ntangiriro za Mutarama 2020.
Abarwayi bagendanaga cyane n'isoko ry'ibikomoka ku mazi rya Hunan, bityo abantu batekereza ko virusi yavuye ku ndwara ya zionis (indwara ihuriye hagati y'abantu n'inyamaswa).
Iyi virusi ikwirakwiza iki cyorezo, izwi nka SARS-CoV-2, ni virusi iherutse kuvumburwa ifite ibimenyetso bisa cyane na Coronavirus y'ikiboko, Coronavirus ya Pangolin na SARS-CoV. Nyuma byamenyekanye ko umuntu wa mbere wagaragaye ibimenyetso byayo ari we wari waranduye ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019, kandi ko nta bucuti busanzwe yari afite n'urugaga rw'ibicuruzwa byo mu nyanja.
Mu itsinda rya mbere ry'ibyabaye mu kwezi kwa cumi na kabiri 2019, byagaragaraga ko bibiri bya gatatu by'ibyabaye mu gihe cy'ubwandu bifitanye isano n'isoko.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe 2020, hari raporo itari yemewe y'ikinyamakuru cya South China Morning Post yagaragaje ko iki cyorezo cyagaragaye ku muntu w'imyaka 55 mu ntara ya Hubei ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo 2019, gishobora kuba ari cyo cyorezo cya mbere cy'indwara. Ku itariki ya 26 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yatangaje ko umubare w'abanduye mu Bushinwa, mu Butaliyani, muri Irani no muri Koreya y'Epfo wiyongereye cyane, ku buryo umubare w'abanduye hanze y'u Bushinwa urenze uw'abanduye mu Bushinwa ku ncuro ya mbere.
Hari igihe nta makuru akomeye yabonetse mu buryo bw'inyongera, cyane cyane mu gihe ibimenyetso by'iyo ndwara byoroheje.
Kugeza ku wa 26 Gashyantare, abantu bafite imyaka mike cyane nibo bagaragaye bafite ubwandu bugabanutse cyane, ku isi hose abagera kuri 2.4% bari bafite imyaka 19 n'iyiri munsi yayo. Patrick Wallace, umujyanama mukuru wa leta y'u Bwongereza mu by'ubuvuzi, yavuze ko kugira ngo umuntu agire ubwirinzi rusange, 60% by'abatuye u Bwongereza bagomba kwandura iyi virusi.
Ni abantu bageragejwe COVID-19 bagaragajwe ko bafite ibimenyetso byemeza ko bafite ikibazo cy'uburwayi, bakurikije amategeko yemewe.
Kuva ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyigeze kigerageza abaturage bacyo basaga 3% kandi politiki y'ibihugu byinshi, harimo n'u Butaliyani, u Buholandi, Esipanye na Suisse, ni uko abantu bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje batagomba kugeragezwa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku wa 16 Werurwe bwagaragaje ko mu Bushinwa, kugeza ku wa 23 Mutarama, abagera kuri 86% by'abanduye COVID-19 bari bataraboneka, kandi ko izo ndwara zitagenzurwa ari zo zateye 79% by'abanduye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku mibare bwashyizwe ahagaragara ku wa 30 Werurwe, bugaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani uri hejuru cyane y'uw'abanduye.
Ingengabitekerezo y'ibanze y'umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 (R0) yari hagati ya 1.4 na 2.4 by'ibanze.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, bwagaragaje ko ari 5.7.
Abantu benshi barwaye COVID-19 barakira.
Ku bantu batari bafite ibimenyetso, igihe cyo kugaragaza ibimenyetso kugeza bapfuye cyatandukanye kuva ku minsi 6 kugeza ku minsi 41, ariko icy'ingenzi ni iminsi 14.
Kuva ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera ku 97.000 baramaze kwandura COVID-19.
Mu Bushinwa, guhera ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, abantu bagera kuri 80% bapfuye bari hejuru y'imyaka 60, 75% bakaba bari bafite uburwayi bw'ibanze, harimo uburwayi bw'umutima n'indwara ya diyabete.
Umubare w'abapfa bazize COVID-19 ni munini cyane kuko utavuga umubare w'abapfa batabanje gupimwa, urugero nko mu ngo cyangwa mu bigo by'abarwayi.
Imibare y'ibanze y'u Butaliyani igaragaza ko umubare w'abapfuye bahitanywe n'icyorezo cya COVID wikubye inshuro 5 kugeza kuri 4 umubare w'abapfuye batangajwe ku mugaragaro.
Umuvugizi w'Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) yemeje ko "" tuzi ko [ibipimo] ari bike cyane kurusha ibipimo by'ukuri". Raporo zivuga ko umubare w'abantu batagira aho bahuriye n'ukuri muri Amerika zemeza ibyo. Ibi bihamya ni bike cyane kurusha ibipimo by'ukuri, akenshi biboneka mu byorezo nk'icyorezo cya H1N1 cy'ibicurane by'ingurube. Urupfu rwa mbere rwemejwe rwabereye i Wuhan ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020".
Urupfu rwa mbere rwo hanze y'u Bushinwa rwabaye ku itariki ya 1 Gashyantare muri Filipine, n'urwa mbere rwo hanze y'u Bufaransa ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, hari abantu barenga mirongo icumi bagaragaye bafite ubumuga bwo kwifata mu buryo bw'igituntu muri Irani, Koreya y'Epfo no mu Butaliyani, hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, habayeho ubwandu mu bihugu birenga mirongo ine no mu bihugu byinshi, ku mugabane wose uretse mu majyepfo y'isi.
Ibipimo by'ibipimo bigenda bitandukana mu bice bitandukanye no mu bihe bitandukanye, kandi bigira ingaruka ku mibare y'ibipimo byakozwe, ubwiza bw'uburyo bwo kwita ku barwayi, uburyo bwo kuvurwa, igihe cy'ubwandu bwa mbere n'imiterere y'abaturage, urugero nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima bw'abaturage.
Nk'uko imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins ibivuga, kugeza ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, ku isi hose umubare w'abapfa n'abandura wari ku kigero cya 6% (abantu 970,39 ku bantu 161,7204).
Ibipimo by'abafite ubumuga bwo kutabona ubumuga mu karere barimo, birahinduka.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa bahitanwa n'iki cyorezo wavuye kuri 17.3% (abantu bafite ibimenyetso byatangira kuva ku itariki ya 1 kugeza ku ya 10 Mutarama 2020) ugera kuri 0.7% (abafite ibimenyetso bitangira kuva ku ya 1 Gashyantare 2020). Ibindi biganishwa birimo: umubare w'abapfa bapfa bazize iki cyorezo (CFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abapfa bazize iki cyorezo, n'uw'abapfa bazize iki cyorezo (IFR IFR), ugaragaza umubare w'abapfa bazize iki cyorezo (bafite ibimenyetso byanduye cyangwa batabifite).
Iyo mibare nta gihe iba ifite, kandi iba ishingiye ku muryango runaka uhereye igihe umuntu yanduye kugeza igihe yongeye kuremba.
Hari abashakashatsi bo muri kaminuza bagerageje kugenzura umubare w'abantu bari mu kigero runaka.
Ikigo cya Kaminuza ya Oxford gifasha mu buvuzi kigaragaza ko umubare w'abapfa ku cyorezo ku isi hose uri hagati ya 0.1% na 0.39%.
Ibipimo by'ibipimo by'ubu bushakashatsi bihuza n'ibisubizo by'igeragezwa ry'ikoranabuhanga rya COVID-19 mu Budage n'igenzura ry'imibare, ndetse n'uko ibipimo by'igeragezwa bihuza n'ibyeragezwa bya CFR.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane ku isi gishobora kugenzurwa.
Igihe cy'ubwandu n'ikiringo cy'iherezo cy'ubwandu ntibiramenyekana kandi bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'aho ubwirakabiri buri.
Maciej Boni wo muri kaminuza ya Penn State yavuze ko ubwandu bw'indwara zandura iyo zitagaragajwe, ubusanzwe buzahoraho igihe runaka nta guhinduka, kandi ko buzagabanuka nyuma y'aho abaturanyi bazaba bamaze guhagarara.
"Ariko ubu nta kintu na kimwe kibasha guhanura neza igihe iki cyorezo kizaba cyarangiye".
Umujyanama mukuru w'ubuvuzi wa leta y'u Bushinwa, Zhang Nansan, yavuze ko niba ibihugu byose bishobora guhuza abantu bose kugira ngo bakurikize inama z'umuryango w'abibumbye z'ubuzima ku bijyanye n'ingamba zo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi, "bishobora kurangira mu kwezi kwa gatandatu".
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, Adam Kucharski wo mu Ishuri ry'Ubuzima n'Ubuvuzi bw'ibihe bidasanzwe mu mujyi wa London, yavuze ko SARS-CoV-2 "igenda ikwira kandi ishobora kumara umwaka umwe cyangwa ibiri".
