William Schaffner wo muri Kaminuza ya Vanderbilt yagize ati ""Ntekereza ko iyi virusi idashobora kuvaho mu buryo bw'inyongera - kuko ari icyorezo cyandura cyane"" kandi ""ishobora guhinduka indwara y'ibihe byose igaruka buri mwaka".""
