Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 bishobora kuba bidasanzwe, kandi abantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso.
Ibimenyetso bibiri bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro (88%) n'ubushyuhe bw'ubumara (68%).
Ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bugabanutse birimo umunaniro, guhumeka (kugabanya guhumeka), gutakaza ibyiyumvo by'ubuhumekero, guhumeka nabi, kubabara mu ngingo no mu ngingo, kuribwa n'umujinya, guhinda umushyitsi, guhinda umushyitsi, guhinda umushyitsi, guhinda umushyitsi, guhinda umushyitsi cyangwa se se se se kwivuza. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rivuga ko hafi umuntu umwe kuri batandatu arwara indwara ikomeye kandi ko ahura n'ubuhumekero.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyatangaje ko ibimenyetso by'ubutagondwa ari ububabare bwo mu mutwe, ububabare bukomeye mu gituza cyangwa mu bwonko, kwiheba mu buryo butunguranye, kubura ibitotsi no gukubita mu maso cyangwa mu kanwa; iyo hari ibyo bimenyetso, ubuvuzi bwihutirwa bugirwa inama.
Bamwe mu bantu banduye bashobora kuba badafite ibimenyetso kandi nta bimenyetso bya kliniki bafite, ariko ibipimo by'imiti byemeza ko banduye, bityo abashakashatsi bagasaba ko abantu bagiranye na bo isano rya bugufi bagenwa neza kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
Umubare w'abarwayi badafite ibimenyetso mu Bushinwa wagereranyijwe ku kigero cya 44% mu mibare mike.
Igihe cyo kuryamana (igihe cyo kuryamana) kigenda gitandukana n'iminsi iri hagati y'icyumweru kimwe n'icyenda; mu bantu benshi, ni iminsi itanu. Urugero rw'ibidashoboka, umubare muto w'abantu banduye COVID-19 batakaza ubumara bwabo bwa mbere wagabanutseho 30% nyuma yaho ugera ku 15%.
Hari amakuru y'ingenzi aherutse kugaragara ku birebana n'uko iki cyorezo cyagaragaye.
Mu byiciro bya mbere, abantu batekereza ko icyorezo cya virusi cyaba cyatewe no guhura n'ibice by'amazi bibonetse mu gihe umuntu avuze, afite inyota cyangwa avuze, ariko iyo umuntu afasheho hagati ya metero 1 na 2 (metero 3 na 6).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko iyo umuntu arimo gusuka nta cyo yambaye, amasuka ashobora kuva kuri metero 4.5 (metero 15) agera kuri metero 8.2 (metero 27).
Hari abavuze ko virusi ishobora no gukwirakwira binyuze mu guturika kw'amazi, urugero nko mu gihe uvuga, kandi ko ishobora kumara igihe kirekire mu kirere.
Ayo matembabuzi ashobora kwinjira mu kanwa cyangwa mu mazuru y'abantu batuye hafi yacu, maze akagerera mu mahaha.
Hari uburyo bwo kuvura nk'ubuyobe no kuvura umutima w'umutima (CPR) bushobora gutuma umwuka uturuka mu kirere, bigatuma umwuka utera.
Iyo ukoraniye ku kintu cyanduye nko ku ruhu, hanyuma ukagikora ku maso, mu mazuru no mu kanwa, indwara ishobora kwandura.
Nubwo hari impungenge ku birebana n'ubwandu bwa virusi y'ibicurane, nta cyo bitwaye.
Leta y'u Bushinwa yanze ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura mu buryo bw'umubiri. Iyi virusi ishobora kwandura cyane mu minsi itatu ya mbere y'ibimenyetso, ariko ishobora no kwanduza abandi mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira no mu bihe by'iherezo ry'icyorezo.
Abantu bageragejwe ko bafite ibimenyetso bya virusi itera SIDA, bigaragaza ko umuntu ashobora kwandura mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bigaragara.
Hari raporo nke z'abantu batagira ibimenyetso byemejwe na laboratwari, ariko hari ibihugu byagiye byemeza ko abantu batagira ibimenyetso byanduye mu gihe cy'iperereza ryakozwe mu gihe bagendaga bakomeza guhura n'abantu.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC) kivuga ko nubwo nta makuru ahari ku buryo bworoshye bwo kwandura indwara, umuntu umwe usanzwe ari umuntu ushobora kwandura abandi bantu babiri cyangwa batatu. Virusi iguma ku butaka amasaha menshi kugeza ku minsi myinshi.
By'umwihariko, virus yabonetse ko ishobora kugaragara ku plastiki (polypropylene) na stainless steel 304, ku kabati umunsi umwe, no ku muringa amasaha arenga ane.
Ariko ibi bihinduka bitewe n'ubushyuhe n'ubushyuhe.
Nta gihamya ihamye igaragaza ko inyamaswa zishobora kwandura virusi ku muntu, nubwo abayobozi b'u Bwongereza bagusaba ko ukaraba intoki nyuma yo guhura n'inyamaswa, nk'uko bikorwa iyo ukoraniye ku bindi bintu byanduye.
Coronavirus 2 syndrome respiratoire acute (SARS-CoV-2) ni virusi nshya yabonetse bwa mbere mu bantu batatu bafite ubumuga bwo mu gituza n'amaboko mu gihe bari bafite ikibazo cy'ubuhumekero n'ibura ry'umwuka mu maraso.
Impamvu zose z'iyi virusi nshya ya Coronavirusi zigaragara mu bindi biremwa bya Coronavirusi. Iyo virusi yiciwe n'isabuni isanzwe, kuko ishyiramo urwego rw'uburinzi. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya bugufi na SARS-CoV.
Birashoboka ko indwara y'indwara ya zioneza cyangwa indwara zihuriyeho n'abantu n'amatungo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku mico ya virusi ya Corona bugaragaza ko virusi ya Corona ifite ubwoko bwa Betacoronavirus n'ubundi bwoko bwa Sarbecovirus (Document B) hamwe n'ubwoko bubiri bw'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima.
Iyi virusi ifite 96% y'ubusabane ku rwego rw'ubwoko bwose bwa genome n'izindi virusi ya coronavirusi y'ikibura (BatCov RaTG13).
Muri Gashyantare 2020, abashakashatsi bo mu Bushinwa basanze mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ubwoko bwa genome, hari itandukaniro ry'amaminosiye imwe gusa hagati y'indwara za pangolin na virusi z'abantu.
Ugereranyije na genome yose kugeza ubu, 92% by'ubwoko bw'imiterere rusange ya coronavirus ya Pangolin na SARS-CoV-2 birahari, ibyo bikaba bidakwiye kugaragaza ko pangolin ari ingenzi mu bakira.
Ubwandu bwa virusi bushobora kumenyekana mu buryo bw'agateganyo hakurikijwe ibimenyetso, nubwo guhamya neza ko aribwo buryo bwo guhangana n'ingorane z'ubwandu bwa polymereze ya transcription reverse chain reaction (Rrt-PCR) cyangwa se CT imaging byemezwa.
Ubushakashatsi bugereranyije uburyo bwo gukora imikorere ya PCR n'ubugenzuzi bw'ikoranabuhanga (CT) i Wuhan bwagaragaje ko CT ifite ubukana bwinshi kurusha PCR, nubwo ari bwo bworoheje cyane, kandi ko ifite imikorere myinshi ihuriye n'ibindi bice by'amabere n'imikorere y'indwara.
Kuva mu kwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, Kaminuza y'Amerika y'Ubuzima bw'Imitsi n'Amashanyarazi (American College of Radiology) yatanze inama y'uko ""Ct idakwiriye gukoreshwa mu gupima cyangwa gupima umurongo wa mbere w'uburwayi bwa COVID-19"."
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryashyize ahagaragara gahunda zitandukanye zo gupima RNA ya SARS-CoV-2, ari na zo za mbere zatangajwe ku itariki ya 17 Mutarama.
Igikorwa cyo gupima gikoresha uburyo bwo guhinduranya imikorere y'urubuga rwa interineti (rRT-PCR).
Igishakishwa gishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero cyangwa amaraso.
Ubusanzwe, ibisubizo bitangwa mu masaha make cyangwa iminsi mike.
Ubusanzwe ibigeragezo bikorwa hakoreshejwe sub-anfi-balamique, nubwo sub-glute ishobora no gukoreshwa. Hari ibigo by'ubushakashatsi n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi byinshi birimo gukora ibigeragezo by'ubushakashatsi ku buryo bwo kumenya abarwayi.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 6 Mata 2020, nta na kimwe muri byo cyari gifite intego zikomeye zo gukoreshwa mu buryo bwagutse.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, hari ikigeragezo cy'ubuvuzi cyakozwe na Cellex cyemerewe gukoreshwa mu bihe by'impanuka gusa n'ibigo by'ubushakashatsi byemewe.
Imyitozo itandukanye y'amashusho mu mashusho ya radioloji n'amashusho ya tomografi (CT) y'abantu bafite ibimenyetso birimo imiterere y'ibirahuri, kandi nta myunamo yo ku ruhande iboneka.
Ishyirahamwe ry'ubuvuzi bw'ibinyabuzima mu Butaliyani (FIRR) ririmo gukusanya amakuru kuri interineti y'ibimenyetso by'indwara z'ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ko hari izindi ndwara z'ubwandu nka adenoviruses, gufata amashusho nta cyizere cya nyuma cya PCR, bishobora gutuma umuntu atabona COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bukomeye bwakozwe mu Bushinwa bugereranyije ibyavuye mu cyuma cy'ubuhumekero bwa CT na PCR, bwagaragaje ko nubwo amashusho y'iyo ndwara akoreshwa gake, ariko ko yihuta kandi ko ashobora gukoreshwa nk'ibikoresho byo gupima mu duce turimo icyorezo.
Imikorere y'imitsi igoranye ishingiye ku bwenge bwa kiremwamuntu, yashyizweho kugira ngo imiterere y'ibimenyetso bya virusi mu mashusho ya radiolojiya na CT.
