Kujya ahantu hatandukanye no ku mubiri nabyo birakorwa kugira ngo umuntu ataza kwandura. Ibihugu byinshi byashyizeho imipaka ku rugendo rw'abantu batacyari ngombwa bajya mu bihugu n'uturere bikunze guhura n'icyorezo.
Icyakora, mu bice byinshi by'isi, virusi imaze kugera ku rwego rwo gukwirakwira mu baturage.
Ibi bivuze ko virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage ndetse ko bamwe mu baturage batazi aho bayanduye n'uburyo bayanduye. Abafasha abandi bashobora kuba barwaye, bagirwa inama yo kwirinda, kwirinda no kwirinda igihe bagirana na bo imibonano mpuzabitsina. Kurinda amakuru y'abantu bagirana na bo imibonano mpuzabitsina ni uburyo bw'ingenzi cyane abayobozi b'ubuzima bakoresha mu kumenya aho bayanduye no kwirinda ko bakwirakwira.
Gukoresha amakuru y'aho telefoni zigera byatewe n'ubutegetsi byatumye abantu bahangayikishwa n'uko umutekano wabo utabungabunga ubuzima, kuko Amnesty International yakoranye n'indi miryango isaga 100 mu itangazo ryasabye ko ibyo bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi bigabanuka.
Porogaramu nyinshi za telefoni zigendanwa zashyizwe mu bikorwa cyangwa zatanzwe ku bushake, kandi kuva ku itariki ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda asaga cumi n'abiri y'abahanga barimo gukora ku buryo bw'ubucuti bwo kurinda ubuzima bwite, nko gukoresha Bluetooth kugira ngo umuntu yinjire muri telefoni igendanwa n'abakoresha hafi y'aho ari.
Nyuma yaho, abakoresha ubutumwa babaza niba baherutse guhura n'umuntu wagize ikigeragezo cya COVID-19. Ibinyoma byogeye ku birebana n'uburyo bwo kwirinda kwandura, urugero nko gukaraba amazuru no gukaraba intoki mu kanwa, nta cyo bimariye.
Nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 rubaho, ariko inzego zitandukanye ziracyakora kugira ngo rubone urukingo.
