Abashyigikiye Shinchongji bari bahuye na Dagu bavuye i Wuhan, bashidikanya ko iyi virusi ishobora kuba yaraturutseho.
Kuva ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bantu 9,336 bari mu idini ry'Abayahudi, abagera kuri 1,261 cyangwa 13% b'abemeraga Imana, bagaragaje ibimenyetso by'indwara. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko hari ku rwego rwo hejuru rw'umuburo ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
