Uburyo bwo gupima bugizwe no gutanga ibimenyetso by'ubushakashatsi ku bashya bavuye mu bihugu bitandukanye binyuze mu porogaramu za mobile, gupima virusi ku magare, ibizamini by'ubushakashatsi bigatangazwa ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bagera ku 20.000 ku munsi.
Nubwo gahunda ya Koreya y'Epfo itari yo gushyira mu kato imijyi yose, yagaragaje ko yagize icyo igeraho mu kurwanya icyorezo.
Abaturage benshi b'igihugu cya Koreya y'Epfo basinye ku nyandiko y'ubucamanza yahanishije ibyaha byakozwe na Moon kubera ibyo bavuga ko ari amakosa ya leta mu gucunga icyorezo, mu gihe abandi basinye bashimira uko yabyitwayemo.
