Ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama, guverinoma ya Trump yatangaje ko hari imimerere y'ubutabazi bw'abaturage, ishyiraho imipaka ku bagenzi binjira mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima bw'abaturage muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, cyatangaje ko cyakoze itsinda ry'imishinga y'igerageza.
Nubwo byagenze bityo ariko, Amerika yatangiye gukora ibizamini by'ubwandu, bituma umubare nyawo w'icyorezo ugenda udasobanuka.
Kubera ko hari amakipe y'igeragezwa yananiwe, yateguwe na Leta y'u Burayi mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare, kubera ko nta cyangombwa cy'igeragezwa cyakozwe na Leta y'u Burayi (biciye mu muryango w'abanyeshuri, amashyirahamwe n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare, n'ibipimo bigabanya abantu bakwifuza gukora ibizamini, ibizamini byakozwe mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (ibikenewe n'ibwirizwa nshingiro ry'umuganga) byafashwe nk'ibitari byiza.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 27 Gashyantare, Washington Post yatangaje ko nta gupima 4000 byakozwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, Atlantic yatangaje ko nta kugeragezwa 14,000 kwakozwe.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko abantu benshi bari bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara n'ibisabwa n'abaganga bategereje ko bagerageza, bategereje amasaha n'iminsi kugira ngo bagerageze. Nyuma y'ibyavuzwe ku ncuro ya mbere ku wa 29 Gashyantare, G. Insley, guverineri w'igihugu, yatangaje ko hari ibintu byihutirwa, ibyo bikaba byari gukurikizwa n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yafunze ku wa 3 Werurwe, mu gihe mu giharage cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, amashuri yo hirya no hino mu gihugu yafunze. Ku wa 6 Werurwe 2020, itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara zo mu rwego rw'indwara zo mu rwego rw'ubuzima bo muri Royal College of London batanze ibipimo by'ingaruka za Coronavirus ku gihugu cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku masezerano yo gutanga inkunga y'inyongera yo gusubiza no kwitegura, aho yari yatanze miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari yo gufasha ibiro by'ishami by'igihugu mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ibigo by'ubucuruzi byashyizeho imipaka ku ngendo z'abakozi, byasubitse inama kandi byashishikarije abakozi gukora imirimo yo mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibihe by'imikino byahagaritswe. Ku wa 11 Werurwe, Trump yashyizeho ibihano by'iminsi 30 ku bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, uretse Ubwongereza, byatangiranye n'itariki ya 13 Werurwe.
Bukeye bwaho, yashyizeho imipaka ku Bwongereza na Irilande.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje imimerere y'ihungabana ku rwego rw'igihugu, bituma imari ya Leta ikoreshwa mu guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ubukene.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibikorwa byinshi byo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika byafunze cyangwa bigabanya amasaha y'akazi bigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe mu bihugu 50 no mu karere ka Columbia. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, New York City yatangaje ko ifite abantu 10.700 banduye Coronavirus, bakaba barenze umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku wa 25 Werurwe, Umuyobozi w'Igihugu yavuze ko kwimakaza abantu mu buryo bw'imibereho myiza bisa n'aho ari ingirakamaro kuko ibigereranywa ko umubare w'abanduye wiyongeraho kabiri byavuye ku minsi 2 bikagera ku minsi 4.7.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, hari abantu 32308 banduye Coronavirus i New York City, abantu 672 bakaba barapfuye bazize iyi virusi. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yatangaje ko ifite umubare munini w'abanduye Coronavirus ugereranyije n'ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, abantu 400335 bamaze kwemezwa muri Amerika, naho abantu 12,841 na bo bapfa.
Amakuru dukesha itangazamakuru yo ku wa 30 Werurwe avuga ko Perezida Trump wa Amerika yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda imishyikirano hagati y'abantu kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, USNS Comfort yafashe ubwato bw'ibitaro bwari bufite ibitanda 1000 i New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zishe abantu 884 bapfuye bazize Coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata muri Leta ya New York, abantu banduye barenga 100.000. Ibiro by'ibanze by'Igihugu by'Igihugu byashyizwe mu kato kubera ko birengagiza iterabwoba no kugabanya amabwiriza abategetsi b'ubuzima n'abahanga bahawe yo guhuza ibitangazamakuru n'ibitangazwa ku bijyanye n'iyi virusi n'ibiro by'icyegera cya Perezida Mike Pence.
Umwanzuro wa Trump wo kuyobora ibibazo by'amashyaka mu nzego z'ubutegetsi wagiye mu bice bibiri.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika banenze uburyo bakoreshaga ibikoresho by'ibanze, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, mu kwinjiza ibintu mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'ingendo z'indege ryateguwe kugira ngo rijye rigaragaza no guhanura ingendo z'icyorezo, ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru cy'ubuvuzi bw'ingendo mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2020.
Mu 2018, abagenzi benshi bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan ni abavuye mu mujyi wa Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei, nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga ry'ubucuruzi bw'indege.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne ni byo byavuzwe ko ari byo by'ingenzi ku bantu bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Mu mijyi 20 ikundwa cyane, Bali ni yo yari iya mbere mu by'ubwiteganyirize, mu gihe mu mijyi ya Australia ari yo yari yiteguye cyane. Australia yatangaje gahunda yo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare.
Ayo magambo yavuze ko kugeza ubu nta makuru menshi y'uko COVID-19 ikomeje kubaho, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo, kugenzura imipaka no guhuza abantu.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, Australia yatangaje imimerere y'ubutagondwa mu rwego rw'ingabo.
Kubera ko hari ingendo zikomeye mu muhanda wa Wuhan n'uwa Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateganyaga ko abaturage n'abakozi ba bya dipolomasi byabo bavanwa muri ako karere, cyane cyane ku buryo bavuye mu gihugu ku buryo bw'indege z'ibanze kandi babiherewe uburenganzira n'abayobozi b'u Bushinwa.
Canada, Amerika, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand ni byo bihugu bya mbere byashyizeho gahunda yo kwirukana abaturage.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazagarura abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Brazil yirukanye 34 mu baturage b'u Brazil cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, hamwe n'abapolonye bane, Umushhinwa n'Umuhindi.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde bavuye mu ndege bari muri Polonye, aho indege y'u Burezili yahagaze mbere yo gukomeza urugendo rwayo rwo kujya muri Brezili.
Abaturage bo muri Brezili bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brezilya.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abakanada 215 (abari mu ndege ya mbere 176 n'abari mu ndege ya kabiri leta ya Amerika yari yaratanze inguzanyo) bavuye i Wuhan bajyanywe muri CFB Trenton, aho bari kumara ibyumweru bibiri bari mu kato.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye abantu 185 bo muri Canada baturutse i Wuhan, yafatiwe mu ndege ya CFB Trenton.
Abayobozi ba Autriche bafashe abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, babajyana mu kigo cy'ibohero cya Christmas Island, cyari cyahindutse icyicaro cyabo cya bwite, aho bamaraga iminsi 14.
Indege yo kuvana muri Nouvelle-Zélande yinjiye mu mujyi wa Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare, aho abagenzi (bari baturutse muri Australia no muri Pasifika) bahagaritswe ku kigo cya Nyanja cya Wangaparoa mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gukura Abanyamerika mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 bo muri Canada bari bavuye mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess bw'imyidagaduro, yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, Leta y'u Buhinde yakoze igikorwa cyo guhanagura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege y'indege y'indege y'indege ya Charter Airlines yo muri Afurika y'Epfo yashubije mu gihugu abaturage 122.
Hakozwe ubugenzuzi bw'ubuvuzi mbere yo kwimuka, maze abaturage bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya Coronavirus baguma aho kugira ngo barinde ibyago.
Abaturage bo muri Afurika y'Epfo gusa bagaragaye ko bageze ku kigero kitari cyiza, ni bo bagarutse mu gihugu.
Ibizamini by'abaturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi b'indege, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bari mu kiruhuko cy'i Ranch, bari mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 bari mu kato no kugenzura mu rwego rwo kwirinda, byagize nabi.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zakuye igice cy'ingabo zayo ku butaka bwa Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku wa 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yavuze ko ibihugu 21 (birimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byashyize inkunga mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri bo mu mashuri makuru yo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu gufasha mu gufasha mu bigo by'abanduye Coronavirus mu Bushinwa. Ikipe y'abashyize hamwe mu karere ka Chicago yashoboye kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa IN95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku wa 30 Mutarama. Ishami ry'ubutabazi rya Direct Relief, rifatanyije na FedEx, ryashyize udupfukamunwa 20,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho byo kwita ku muntu harimo imyenda n'imyenda, ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, ryatumye ikigo cy'ubutabazi bw'indege gitwara abantu mu buryo bw'impanuka, i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bahawe miliyoni 100 z'amadolari Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) kugira ngo bishyireho amafaranga yo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku nkingo n'imiti y'ubuvuzi, no gushyigikira "abantu bafite ibyago muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo".
Interaksyon yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare, leta y'Ubushinwa yahaye Filipine amasiki ibihumbi 200, nyuma yaho umuyobozi w'inteko ishinga amategeko Richard Gordon yohereje miliyoni 3.16 z'amasiki i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix-Rouge de Singapour yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga y'amadolari miliyoni 2.26 ku Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwatanze agapfukamunwa ka miliyoni imwe, u Bushinwa bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birenga toni 13, u Bushinwa bwatanze ingofero za miliyoni 18 z'amakanzu y'ubuvuzi, u Budage bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birenga miliyoni 10 harimo imyenda yihariye, naho Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatanze ingofero za miliyoni 17.8 z'ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, ndetse zisezeranya inkunga y'amadolari miliyoni 100 ku bihugu byugarijwe n'iyo ndwara.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abahanga mu gufasha u Butaliyani kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umucuruzi w'icyamamare Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho by'igeragezwa miliyoni 1.1 n'amasiki miliyoni 6 n'ibikoresho by'imyenda 60,000 by'uburinzi byatanzwe n'ishyirahamwe ry'ibihugu by'Afurika, mu mujyi wa Addis Ababa muri Etiyopiya.
Yatumye muri Panama ibikoresho 5000 byo gupima, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'ibikoresho 5 byo guhumeka.
""Twahawe ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi na Canada. U Buholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque byatangaje impungenge ku masiki n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe n'Ubushinwa".
Urugero, u Esipanye yahisemo kugabanya gukoresha ibikoresho byo kugerageza byakozwe n'Ubushinwa, bifite uburebure bwa 30%, mu gihe u Buholandi bwagaragaje ko hari amasiki y'Ubushinwa arenga ibihumbi 600.
Ububiligi bwirinze kwakira udupfukamunwa 100,000 tudakoreshwa, kubera ko abantu batekerezaga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa ariko ko twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika yongeye guhabwa.Ku wa 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangiye ibikorwa by'ubutabazi bwihutirwa ku bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) rishimiye imihati y'abayobozi b'u Bushinwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryerekanye ko ibi bintu byari bimeze nk'icyorezo cya SARS mu 2002-2004, aho abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bagirizwa ko bahishe amakuru, ibyo bigira ingaruka mbi ku bikorwa byo kwirinda no kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi, kandi muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo, guverinoma y'u Bushinwa "yafashe ingamba zo gutanga amakuru mu rwego rwo kwirinda icyorezo cy'indwara mbere y'ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya w'izuba".
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, uhagarariye OMS, Goodin Gali, mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ibanze cyo gushyiraho itegeko ribuza gutwara abantu mu mujyi wa Wuhan, yatangaje ko "ibi bitari inama y'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima", ariko ko "ibimenyetso by'ingenzi cyane bigaragaza ko twiyemeje guhagarika iki cyorezo aho kiza cyane kurusha ahandi hose", avuga ko "ari ikintu kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima bw'abaturage". Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko abantu bagenewe mu mahanga no mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyihutirwa mu rwego mpuzamahanga, ari nacyo cya gatandatu cy'iki cyorezo kuva mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya virusi ya Influenza cyabayeho mu mwaka wa 2009.
Tedros Adhanom, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima, yavuze ko PHEIC "ibanze ku iterambere ry'ubuzima ku isi, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'ayigereranyije n'ay'abari mu bihugu bifite gahunda mbi zo kwita ku buzima".
Mu gusubiza ku bihano by'ingendo, Tedros yatangaje ko ""nta mpamvu yo gukora ibikorwa bidakenewe bibangamira ingendo n'ubucuruzi ku isi"" kandi akomeza agira ati ""OMS ntishyigikira kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".""
Ku wa 5 Gashyantare, Umuryango w'Abibumbye wasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gufasha ibihugu bifite amikoro make mu kwitegura ibikorwa by'ingamba, kandi wibutsa ko hari hakenewe ubufasha mu bihugu "bitagira uburyo bwiza bwo gutahura abantu banduye cyangwa bafite ibimenyetso".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko ""dukomeye nk'abari mu kaga cyane mu mishyikirano tugirana"" asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga ""guhora ushyiraho imari cyangwa ugashyiraho amafaranga menshi nyuma yaho".
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko umunyamabanga mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, Antonio Guterres, yemeye gukoresha ""imikorere myiza y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo"".
"Ibyo byatumye itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'amacakubiri ryihutirwa gushyira mu bikorwa gahunda yo guhuza ibisubizo by'umuryango w'abibumbye, rivuga ko rizajya ryemererwa "gukora cyane ku bijyanye n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi, mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gushyiraho ubuhanga bwazo mu nzego z'imibereho ya rubanda, ubukungu n'ingaruka z'icyorezo".
Ku itariki ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'umurimo w'ubumwe ryashyizwe mu bikorwa riyobowe n'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima, WHO, kugira ngo rijye mu Bushinwa rifasha mu gucunga mu gihugu no gupima "uburemere n'ubukana bw'iki cyorezo", rihuza n'amasomo, inama n'inzego z'igihugu, ndetse n'abasura mu rwego rwo gupima "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza mu ntara, mu ntara/mu nzego z'ubuyobozi, harimo n'ibice by'umujyi n'icyaro". Ku itariki ya 25 Gashyantare, umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima wavuze ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya Coronavirus" kandi ko hakiri kare ko cyitwa icyorezo, ariko ko ibihugu "bikwiye kuba biteguye".
Mu gusubiza iki cyorezo cyagendaga giyongera muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abakozi bahuje inshingano muri icyo gihugu kugira ngo bagenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko ibipimo by'icyorezo cya Coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi bivuye ku "kirenga" bikagera ku "kirenga cyane".
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi ushinzwe gahunda y'ihungabana ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima, mu itangazo, yatanze umuburo agira ati ""Icyo ni ukuri ku butegetsi bwose bw'isi: ni ukwikangura".
"Virus iri mu nzira, kandi ugomba kuba witeguye, ukamenya ko igisubizo cyiza gishobora gufasha isi kwirinda ""kuyiyongeraho""".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru y'ubu atari yo azatuma abategetsi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza ko hari icyorezo ku isi kuko ibyo bitangaza bivuze ko ""dufata ko umuntu wese ku isi azandura iyi virusi".""
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa WHO yavuze ko "Iri shami ryita ku mibare iteye ubwoba y'icyorezo n'uburemere bw'icyorezo, ndetse n'imibare iteye ubwoba y'uko nta cyo ikora". WHO yanenzwe cyane kubera ibyo bita ko ari icyorezo, harimo gutangaza ko hashyizweho igihe cyo gushyiraho ihungabana ry'ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi mu cyiciro cy'icyorezo".
Iyi myifatire ya politiki yari irimo ikirego cy'ubujurire ku muyobozi mukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima, Tedros Adhanum, ku gitekerezo cye cyo gutanga imihoho, cyari cyashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733,000 kuva ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere z'umuryango w'abibumbye ku burenganzira bw'ikiremwamuntu zemeza ko uburenganzira bw'abantu bubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'abahanga ryavuze ko ibikorwa byo kurokora abantu bigomba gukorwa ku giti cyabo, kandi ko ari inshingano ya leta.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kuba nta mafaranga cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bidakwiye kuba impamvu yo kurobanura ku butoni ku bantu runaka.
Abahanga bemeje ko buri wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abatishoboye, abafite ubumuga bwo kutabona, abimukira, abatagira aho baba, abafite ubuzima butari bwiza, abafunzwe n'abandi bakeneye inkunga ya leta.
Ibigo bya leta mpuzamahanga birimo gucunga ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage z'iki cyorezo cya COVID-19.
OECDC yashyizeho urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru y'igihe kandi yuzuye ku bijyanye n'imiyoborere y'ibisubizo mu bihugu byo ku isi ndetse n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku miyoborere yo gukomeza ubuzima bwiza no kubaka ubukungu bw'isi kugeza ku gusuzuma ingaruka z'imyirondoro n'ingamba zo gukora ingendo, Digital Hub irimo gukurikirana politiki y'igihugu (uko ibihugu bitabira iki kibazo) igamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku byakozwe n'ibindi no korohereza igisubizo gikoranabuhanga ku bibazo bya Coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yashyigikiwe n'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bwongereza Michael Gove na Eduardo Bolsonaro, umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil, Jair Bolsonaro, kubera ko yagabye icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane cyatangiye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abayobozi b'inteko z'u Bushinwa (CPC) benshi barirukanywe kubera ko bari bagenzura ibikorwa byo gushyira mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko nta mwete bagaragaje ku bijyanye n'uko abanyapolitiki bitabiriye iki cyorezo muri utwo duce.
Bamwe mu banenga ibivugwa muri iyi nyandiko bavuga ko icyo gikorwa cyari icy'umutekano ku mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti ryo mu Bushinwa, Xi Jinping, mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
