Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzihumeka mu gikoresho cyo guhumeka, byagaragariye ko ubwandu bw'ibinyabuzima ku ntoki bwazamutseho 194% n'ubw'intoki 254%.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe hari umwuka w'umwuka byatumye umubare w'udukoko tugize intoki ku ntoki wiyongeraho 42% n'utundi 15% ku ntoki.
Nyuma yo gukaraba no gukaraba intoki n'umwambi w'impapuro, umubare w'udukoko twagabanutseho ku kigero cya 76 ku ijana ku munsi ku ntoki no ku kigero cya 77 ku ijana ku munsi ku kigero cy'intoki. Abahanga bakomeje gukora ibizamini kugira ngo barebe niba hari ubwandu bushobora guhitana abandi bakoresha ubwiherero n'ibidukikije byo mu bwiherero kubera gukoresha uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo gukaraba.
Airjet air dryer, ikura umwuka mu modoka ku muvuduko wa metero 180 ku gitebe (ibirometero 650 ku isaha), ishobora guhumeka uturemangingo two mu ntoki no mu bikoresho, kandi ishobora guhumanya abasoresha ubwiherero n'ibidukikije by'ubwiherero ku metero 2.
Gukoresha umwuma ushyushye w'amaboko, byatuma mikoroorganzyme zikwirakwira ku gipimo cya metero 0.25 z'umwuma.
Igitabo cyo kumesa amaboko nticyagaragaje ko cyakwirakwizaga uturemangingo. Mu mwaka wa 2005, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na TÜV Produkt und Umwelt bwagaragaje uburyo butandukanye bwo kumesa amaboko.
