Kwirinda ibyago byo guhura na COVID-19 mu kazi
Kugenzura ibyago mu kazi bya COVID-19 bisobanura gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bwo kwirinda no kwirinda impanuka z'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura ibyago mu kazi bihuje neza n'aho ukorera n'akazi ukora, kandi bigenda bihinduka bitewe n'uko umuntu agenzura ibyago by'ibanze by'ubwandu, uburemere bw'uburwayi mu baturage n'ibyago by'umukozi wese ushobora guhura na COVID-19.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'ikigo cy'ubuzima n'umutekano muri Amerika (OSHA), ibikorwa bifite ibyago bike cyane bifite umubare muto w'imishyikirano y'akazi n'abaturage n'abandi bakozi, birasabwa ko byitondera ingamba zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo gukaraba intoki, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukoresha udupfukamunwa no gukora isuku no guhanagura ibikorwa by'akazi.
Muri ibyo bigo harimo n'ibyo ku rwego rwo hagati, aho usanga abantu badakeneye guhura cyane n'abantu bakekwaho cyangwa banduye COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba bafite ibyago bitewe no guhura n'abaturage cyangwa se gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibyo bikubiyemo abakozi bagirana na rubanda imishyikirano mu bigo nk'amashuri, ahantu ho gukorera abantu benshi, ndetse no mu maduka manini amwe n'amwe.
Kugenzura ibyago by'iyi kipe, uretse ingamba zo kubanza zo kwirinda kwandura, harimo guhumeka umwuka ukoresheje ibipimo by'umwuka bikora neza, kwirinda inyota no kubona ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku muntu kugira ngo ahangane n'umuntu urwaye COVID-19.
OSHA ifata abakozi b'ubuzima n'ubuvuzi bagirana isano n'abantu bakekwaho COVID-19 nk'abakora imirimo ikomeye, kandi iyo bakoresheje uburyo bwo kubyara Aerosol cyangwa gufata ibipimo by'abantu bakekwaho cyangwa banduye COVID-19, ibyo bigatuma barushaho kugira ibyago byinshi.
Muri ibyo byiciro harimo n'ibipimo by'ibyago by'akazi bifitiye abo bakozi, harimo n'ibipimo by'ubuhanga, urugero nk'ibyumba bifite umwuka mubi n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi by'umuntu bikenewe mu kazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba badahari ku kazi kubera uburwayi, kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya kurwara.
Uburyo bwo gucuruza bushobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibikenewe ndetse no mu buryo bwo kubikoresha (urugero nko kugura mu masaha y'isaha y'icyumweru cyangwa mu buryo bwo gutanga ibyangombwa cyangwa serivisi zo gutwara ibinyabiziga).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibicuruzwa mu turere tw'isi twazahajwe na COVID-19 bishobora kuba ikibazo. Gutegura uburyo bwo kwirinda no gusubiza indwara zandura bishobora gukoreshwa.
Mu migambi, hagaragaramo ibyago by'akazi n'akazi, harimo ibiva mu byo umuntu ahura na byo, ibyago by'akazi mu muryango no mu rugo, ndetse n'ibyago by'akazi ku mukozi wese, harimo n'uburwayi bw'igihe kirekire.
Mu mugambi harimo uburyo bukwiriye bwo kugenzura ibyo bibazo n'ingamba zo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Imishinga yo gutegura no guhangana n'indwara zandura ishobora gukorwa hashingiwe ku nama z'igihugu cyangwa z'aho uherereye.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo ni ukugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara hagati y'abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara ziterwa n'indwara, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka zidakwiriye ku zindi nzego mu mitego yabo y'ibikoresho.
Ubukana bw'iki cyorezo bugira ingaruka ku bantu, aho ibikorwa biherereye, ku buryo abantu bakira ibyo babwirwa.
Urwego rw'ubugenzuzi bw'ibiza ni ingengabihe ikoreshwa cyane mu kubungabunga ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi kugira ngo ingengabize ry'ibiza rigendeye ku kigero cy'ingaruka.
Aho hatariho uburyo bwo kugabanya ibyago bya COVID-19, uburyo bwo kugenzura ubwubatsi, ubundi bukaba ari ubw'ubuyobozi, ndetse n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi, ni bimwe mu bikoreshwa cyane mu kugenzura.
Ubugenzuzi bw'ubuhanga ni ugukura abakozi mu kaga k'akazi, nta gushingira ku myitwarire y'umukozi, kuko bishobora kuba ari byo byonyine bifasha.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuyobozi ni ibintu byatanzwe mu nama cyangwa mu mikorere y'akazi, kandi abakozi cyangwa abakozi bagomba kubikurikiza.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyawe (PPE) bifite ingufu nke kugenzura ibikorwa by'ubuyobozi n'ubuhanga, ariko bishobora kwirinda bimwe mu byago.
Buri bwoko bwa PPE bugomba guhitamo uburyo bukwiriye bwo gushyirwamo (urugero, udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi), bukoreshwa buri gihe, bukagenzurwa, bukoreshwa, bukagarurwa, bukongera gufungurwa, bukagororwa, bukongera gushyirwaho niba bikenewe, cyangwa bukagororwa kugira ngo buzihishe ubwandu.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'Ikigo cy'Ubuzima n'Umutekano mu Buryo bw'Akarere (OSHA) muri Amerika, abakozi bafite ibyago bike cyane, bafite umubare muto w'imishyikirano y'akazi n'abaturage cyangwa abandi bakozi, ni bo bafite ibyago bike cyane.
